Title: Managed GPX
Description:
Managed GPX is a managed C#-implementation for manipulating, evaluating and displaying GPX files. An interface to OSM will be also included.

The library consists of two parts: 
- Base API for reading, writing and reporting GPX-Files
- GUI-Library for WPF-Rendering
